original: Öijer, Oscar Vilhelm, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 29/3/10 i Törnevalla, Ös-tergötl. 1., av O. L. Öijer o. Hilma Carolina Pettersson. G. 37 m. Elsa El-vine Östholm. Barn: Göran f. 39, Christina 41. — Stud:ex. i Linköp. 29, tandl :kand. 32, tandläk. 35. Assist, i Sthlm 35-36, däreft. praktik i Reftele, skoltandl. i Reftele o. Västboås, praktik i Linköp. sed. 42.
translated: Öijer, Oscar Vilhelm, dentist, Linköping, born on 29/3/10 in Törnevalla, Östergötland, 1st district, son of O.L. Öijer and Hilma Carolina Pettersson. Married in 1937 to Elsa El-vine Östholm. Children: Göran, born in 1939, Christina, born in 1941. Completed high school in Linköping in 1929, graduated as dental candidate in 1932, became a dentist in 1935. Worked as an assistant in Stockholm from 1935-1936 and then practiced in Reftele. Also worked as a school dentist in Reftele and Västboås. Started practicing in Linköping in 1942.
